'''Pre-game''' is a word used by many high school and college students in such ways as, "Where are we gonna pre-game tonight?" or "Did you guys pre-game before you got to the party?".  In a pre-gaming event, several friends get together to drink before going out to a party.  The goal of pre-gaming is to have a buzz before going out for the night.

